rComments: He is just adorable. So sad he left UTM .... *sigh*

Very charismatic, comprehensive teacher. He is expansive but accessible, eloquent and knowledgeable. He seems genuinely engaged with the material and his students. He's also completely funny, adorable and sweet, I would take all of his classes if I had the time.

I love him! He's totally helpful! He is interesting to listen to and hes just so darn cute! I have taken 3 classes with him and I would continue if I weren't graduating! He's amazing! Even helped me with a reccomendation letter for Teacher's college!

One of the best English teacher's I've had besides DiPietro. He always encourages students to put out their ideas. He takes your points and expands upon the elements at the heart of the novel with incredible finesse.
He's very encouraging and extremely helpful. His sweet personality makes him my favourite prof in the eng department!
